aaj mai bahut kush hu, aaj bahut salo baad dumrao ki chatti se prashidh chausa ke apne kumhara muhhla ja rha hu. aaj kitni sari purani yade awichal hi yaad aa rhi hai. apne digaha jhund ke baccho ke sath masti aur ho halla karna. paas ke pokhre jakar roj saam ko bansi dalkar machari pakarna. roj saam khet ke khule maidan me bat baal, gilli danda aur pakada pakadi khelna.
sham ko suraj ke dhalte hi ghar ki aur daud lagana. aur apne pyare se ghar ke bade se aangan me khat pe baith kar bhaio ke sath padhai karna. padhai ke samay thandi thandi hawao me laltain ki roshni ke bich apne kitab me kahaniya aur kavitae padhna, gadit karna aur angraji padhana kitna yaad aata hai. mitti ke chulhe par maa ki banai garam garam roti sabji khana.

aur raat ke 8-9 bajte hi sare gao ka sannate me dub jana.
